DESCRIPTION:
Cassandra JMeter plugin supports all the jmeter functions and variable hence making it a right fit to generate data into cassandra. You can also validate the data and measure performance/throuhput of a cassandra cluster.

DETAILS:

MAVEN:
JMeter plugin needs the following jar's to be present for it to compile, but they are not published in the public repo hence do the following.

mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=org.apache.jmeter -DartifactId=ApacheJMeter_core -Dversion=2.5.1 -Dfile={Your base Dir}/lib/ApacheJMeter_core.jar -Dpackaging=jar -DgeneratePom=true
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.netflix -DartifactId=astyanax -Dversion=1.22.0 -Dfile={Your base Dir}/lib/astyanax-1.22.0.jar -Dpackaging=jar -DgeneratePom=true


